@startuml navigation-shell-state
' Context: navigation
' Profile: client
' Revision: 2026-07-19
' Statechart: NavigationShellState + ConversationScope

title Navigation — shell e ambito conversazione

state InboxVisible : committedScope = null
state ChatOpen : committedScope = (owner, peer, epoch)
state GroupShell : committedScope = null

[*] --> InboxVisible

InboxVisible --> ChatOpen : OpenConversation\nCommitConversationScope
InboxVisible --> GroupShell : EnterGroupShell\nInvalidateConversationScope

ChatOpen --> InboxVisible : CloseConversation\nInvalidateConversationScope
ChatOpen --> ChatOpen : OpenConversation (altro account/peer)\nInvalidate → Commit

GroupShell --> GroupShell : OpenGroupConversation
GroupShell --> GroupShell : LeaveGroupConversation

note right of ChatOpen
  Un solo [ConversationScope] commesso.
  Messaging legge solo da qui.
  activePeer in view-state è proiezione UI.
end note

@enduml
